\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Aye, the bowl of porridge, we
 had two basins. One with milk and one with porridge and we used to put the spoon in the - porridge and then into the milk and cover it up and then - you'd to wipe your ears out with it. Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Apart from eggs you didn't normally have a good breakfast but you think your father would perhaps have bacon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Aye, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Your main meal was in the middle of the day, you had tea to drink at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 
breakfast time}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 , for your main meal you had chicken sometimes and with living on a farm you had plenty of good food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Chicken, aye. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What sort of puddings did you have at lunchtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 A suet puddings. Or jam - jam }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 rollies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you have anything to drink at dinnertime?
