\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brother and sister in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
