\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh we always were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You always got on well together did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you quarrel at all with your brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did they say you should hit back or not if another child hurt you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - oh yes, they told me - father told me, he said, you hit him, I - I used to and all. Didn't half used to wallop 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
Well they thought I'd been all right but - you know, with being in the Army a good bit you know - that - they - they did - always used to write and that you know. Thought I was all right like, I was all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did your parents bring you up to consider certain things important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh they used to tell you which was - which was - what was right and wrong you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Any particular thing they told you you shouldn't do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 They told me I hadn't to steal. Or owt - anything like that. And I never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Anything else they thought you should do or not do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So what kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Hundred percent.
