\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You know - very good. Good living.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What do you consider good living to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well I think - respect the law, respect God and - and - I used to - feed hor
ses, I tell you - when I had horses you always were taught - to feed - feed them as you feed yourself. You know, respect - if you feel hungry the horse is }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 hungry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 . You feed it at a certain time. And if it's dry and you tracking and all this you know - alway
s undone the girth, take the bits out and all that you know and drink - give 'em water when you were dry. Proper respect for horse. And the more you - I - oh, I used to have a horse called Bruiser, kick - it used to take - we had to clip him in his stocks
,
 in the Army, clip him in his stocks and take four blacksmiths to shoe him. And I could do anything with him, he - kiss - I could kiss him, take him pat-a-cakes on a morning in the stable. Put 'em in me mouth. Oh I could do anything with him. Yes. He coul
d - he could - he could kick anything on one foot. He could. He was terrible. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did your parents think of swearing, were you allowed to swear or did they swear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 They'd always listen to you would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
