 to drive to Darlington, and she used to call me Buttons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You just came with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, I - I had to take the horse, when I was - with me dad, and - I was only about - eleven. I used to take her to the stables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You told me that sometimes you went to school on a horse?
