\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
