\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you feel about your teachers there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 All right. They were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did they ever teach you good manners or to be tidy or to be punctual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh yes, you had to be - O.K. there like. It was all right like. Old Cleghorn was the master. Cleghorn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were they keen on the way you spoke, did they correct your speech?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 If you did anything the teachers disapproved of at the Central school what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Get the cane.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 For what sort of offences did they get the cane?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Fighting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Was there a lot of fighting going on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Not a lot. I used to do a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Are you thinking of any particular occasion you had a fight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
Yes. We were playing football in the schoolyard one day. And a bloke ran into me, knocked me down - for accident like. So I - when we were marching round at play - at playtime - I was marching behind this 
bloke, you know, used to play football and one thing and another, just tipped him under the - step and he - missed his step and down he fell. I got the cane }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 for}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  that. Aye. Howard Treater they called him, he played football for Darlington, aye, this fellow 
and - I'd done something one day and - I used to play for the school at football. Gets hold of me hand, he says, come here. And he pulled him - pulled me to him see, like that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 W}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 hen he pulled me to him - I kicked him underneath the foot, right on the toe - right under there. You know, going forward quick, he never played for Darlington that weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You put him out of action did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Put him out of action.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You'd have a lot in common though if he was a footballer wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - Shaw they called him, Shaw. Nice fellow like but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did your parents ever visit this school or meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 NO.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did they still ask you what you did at a school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, they never used to bother much. They knew I could read or write so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Just the same - similar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment form the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were there any gangs or groups in this school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No groups, no gangs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Any children who were left out of things,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So how old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I was fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. Didn't have a chance. I was two year there mind. I'd be fourteen when I left. Aye. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No I don't think R would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you attend any part time education afterwards, did you go to ay evening classes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Do you think you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 benefited}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes,. running milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 'Cos he knew me. Aye, he knew me and all. Over here. Over here, next door to me father's garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What exactly did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Take milk out in the morning. Milk round. In cans. You know, big gallon can and -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did you take it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 On a float. Milk float. Horse and milk float.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were you just helping someone else, were you helping the farmer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I - I was on me own, I used to do it
 on me own. He used to come down - we - he - he; was a terrible fellow for the women talking, he was always talking, worse than me. And I used to be along the police station, he would meet us over road, have you finished? Aye, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What hours did you work, what time did you start doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh about seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 About an hour and a half it took me. Then I went to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you do it on Sundays and Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever have any days off at all from that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No I don't think so.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Half a crown I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I couldn't do no other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 A shilling I think. Give her a shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What was it spent on, what would she do with the shilling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What would you do with the one and six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I spent it. Sweets. Sweets, that's about all, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh fine, I was boss.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 O.K.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 He was very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did they have any other young boys helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 His son. But he was younger than me see, he couldn't go with the float. Too young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did he help in another way, what did he do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well just messed about, he was only about eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you feel about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Liked it. I used to milk and all. Oh yes. I used to milk when I was six years old. Aye. Used to - used to hard work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 It doesn't look as if it's done you any harm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh it's kept us fit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did this part time job alter your attitude to school in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you do any other part time jobs before you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What was your first full time job, what did you do when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Went to the Whessoe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You were a labourer there up 'til the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you got that job at Whessoe?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Through my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What exactly did you have to do in this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I was helping a - plater. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What hours did you work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Six - six o'clock in the morning. Six 'til twelve. One 'til five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 That was long hours wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you have any weekends off, what about Saturdays and Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 We had Saturday afternoons off. And Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you have any holidays with pay from there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Do you remember what you were paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes, eleven bob.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 Did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No I didn't. I asked for a rise - I says - smith the foreman, I said, what about the rise, I'm doing a man's job here? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Ah, but he says, look at you, you know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 He said, men with families only eighteen shilling a week. Aye. 
I said, I do more work than them. I was strong as hunter and all. And - Dick Rush, my - boiler smith, he wouldn't have nobody else. He said, I'll see what I can do, I'll shove two bob in. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Shove
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  two bob in me tin. And after that - I joined Army after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes, ten shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did you spend your money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Taking the tart out. The tart out. Yes, they - go around a bit you know.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\tx4860\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid8864990 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
How did you get on with the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 other}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  people you worked with at Whessoe?
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid8864990 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Easy.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were they all good people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did your employer treat you, who would be the boss there that you were in contact with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 He - Contes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 He was O.K.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did he treat you, did you ever come into contact with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh I never - he often was - you know, round about like but he never said owt to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you feel about this work, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did you do after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What in the Army, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So you left Whessoe and went in the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Where did you go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I went in the - Army Service Corps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were you stationed around here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, Manchester. Aye. Had to go through a course th
ere up riding school - horses you know. Oh doing all sorts of tricks like the circus. Aye, jumping and - and of course I was leading the section and there was the youngest one in the section and being used to horses was a lucky to me, I was always lead. }
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Aye}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 . A }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 rough}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
 riding sergeant Major - used to have a long whip you know. He didn't use it on us like but - he thought to himself, well - I'm the best one of the lot, see, and I used to do the figure eight and all sorts and always used to follow. And a lot of 
those that was there you know and there was about twenty of us at the time in the section, and - they used to fall off and that. And then - then I went to Fleetwood to ferry me across. Well I was in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Durham\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  there you know. And of course, hitting a target to me was a mickey. I was first class shot.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Had you done some shooting on the farm before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, not on the farm. But - I done it in the Territorials when I was here, two years in 19 - 1910 to 1912. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 Aye,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  well - it was before I joined the Regi
ment, I joined the Regiment in '12. To '14. I was - from 10 - 1910 to - I was at two camps and going on to a third when the war }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 broke}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  out. If I hadn't have joined the - if I hadn't have joined the Regulars see, I would - I would have been in the war with the Territorials see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So 1910 to 1912 you were working }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Whessoe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  but you were in the Territorials?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 And then you went in the Regular Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes. 19 - 1912 to '14. And I was just coming out - I was coming out on the 12th - 25
th of August, and we declared war August the 3rd or something, and - I had me civvies and everything and - had to leave them. I got the - the Colonel's housemaid looked after them for us 'til I got 'em sent home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So you were right in the thick of things then were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I was right I - over there. I've just been watching it on telly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 When you were in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Teas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  how often did you go there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh we used to go three times a week. Then we used to go camping. We went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 
Richmond}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  - first year, 1910, 1911 to Scarborough, and 1912 was to Conway, but I was in the Regulars then,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did Whessoe's let you have time off to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - yes, they let you have it for your holidays, you used to take it for a fortnight holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did the Territorials pay you at all?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, we didn't get any money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Nothing when you were in camp?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
You were when you were in camp, so much when you were in camp but you didn't get any-not like they do now you know. We got nothing for doing - just your uniform, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What made you join the Regular Army?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
Well, I liked the - liked the Army. I liked the Army. So I went in. There was now much there for me really. I didn't - I wasn't really - we - I didn't get any more money, I got less money going 
in the Army, we had a shilling a day there. Aye. Shilling a day then, yes. I - I got allowance for me mother when the war was on. I was a full corporal like, when I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 got made}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  a corporal I - I used to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 allow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  me mother was it - either five or seven shilling. A
nd she put it away for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 When you were in the Regular Army what sort of routine did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
Oh well stables in the morning. Oh you done everything you know. The Army. Musketry, drill. Shooting. And then the horses, see, we had horses all the time. Ride horses and - jumping horses and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you get any free time at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
Oh yes, you got - you were finished at - oh just when you finished your job. You might be at nine o'clock at night. Or it might be four, it might be teatime, you maybe get afternoon off. But still you had to go the stables. See, look after the horses.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever get a half day clear, did they ever allow you time off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Very rare. Bar when we were playing football. Aye. That's why I have to play football. If y
ou're not - not anything - aye. And then there was the guards to do you know. They come round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How much leave did they give you in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What were you paid, a shilling a day? Did you feel that was a fair wage or not, because you were kept as well weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well I don't - it was the wage of the generation then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did your mother do with the money you sent her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Saved it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did she save it up for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes, she saved it up for me. And she got it when I got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did you get on with the other people you worked with, what other sort of fellows were in the Army with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - all right, champion. Oh never had no trouble at all. We used to box - I used to box all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you like being in the Army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes. See with being in the Territorials - it learned us a lot before - discipline and all that you know, I was corporal about five year.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Then you stayed to the end of the war did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I went to France. I was knoc
ked out - I was sleeping with a horse in - 25th of march - about the third - after me twenty-first birthday, five days after I was kicked with a horse in the face - 1914 - '15 and - I was in Newcastle at Armstrong's College on the first of April.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 In hospital?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Hospital. Aye. And then I went in - I was there two month and then I went to - Branchforth Castle, Lady }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Boges's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  place. Branchforth. Convalescent. A big castle over there. Good food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 When did you go back to the front line again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No
, I went - I was sent down to - Aldershot, I had a leave, fortnights leave. I went down to Aldershot. And we transferred to the - I had to go to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Basingstoke}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  to join a - Eleventh Division who were going to the Dardanelles. And - I missed the draft. I got off that, and we went to Salonica it was changed over. Some men - I went to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 Greece}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were you there until the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I was there 'til the end of the war. Three year - I was there three year - nearly three year. Well there wasn't much fight
ing there, I had malaria, the pension for malaria there. I've got a pension for malaria.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What jobs have you done since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I went to the railway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What did you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I was a slinger. For twenty-eight year, then the remaining part, twelve year, I was welding, electric welder.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So you became a skilled workman then }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 did you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Does that bring us up to when you retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you serve an apprenticeship or training period for any of your jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. Served - training when I went to be a welder. Short of welders at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes, N.U.R.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you take part in any of its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes, cricket. Railway cricket. And of course football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you do anything for the administration side, were you a party worker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different interests
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - they were - if you done your work you were O.K.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Would you say they had the same interests or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes. They had interest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you feel there were divisions of interest among workers, some people say that in those days there was a
 great division between a trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 There wasn't a - as regards as - being personal or owt like that. But otherwise }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid203415\charrsid8407452 there might}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  have been with a - you couldn't - they never showed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 But in a works did you feel there was a difference between a trained craftsmen and a labourer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh I don't think so. I don't think so.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No, it keeps you fit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you continue to live at home after you left school, you did for a little while didn't you, you left school at fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I left school at fourteen, was in the Army by eighteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 So you had four years living at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did starting full time work change }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 your}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did it change your relationship with your brother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you spend your Sundays any differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you still go to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You stopped then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Aye,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I used to go to Sunday school when - before I left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you still continue to go to Sunday school when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Could you tell me what your views were?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 \{ILLEGIBLE\} at all, only voted for - what me father voted for, Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Was that the only reason, because your father voted liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 I had a vote but I didn't vote. See I were in - I was in the Army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever feel under any pressure from anyone to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Were you a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time when you were a schoolboy, y
ou played football and you played cricket and you went to the races with your father, did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way or did you do different things now that you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh I still - when I left school do you mean? Ye
s. Oh used to go to the - I used to go to the races. Still went the races. And played football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you still go for cycle rides?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Cycle rides, walking. And the dogs. Swimming. Oh aye. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Where did you swim?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 The baths and round the Tees. Cleasby Deeps. Oh aye. Well I was a swimmer in the Army you know. Aye. I were a swimmer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you go out in the evening at all, between fourteen and eighteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh yes, I was always - always -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Where did you used to go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well walks and - up at the - Institute. Railway Institute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 What sort of things did they do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well used to play cards and - billiards and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Who would you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well I'd a pal and he's dead now and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Just one particular boy friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 There was no girls allowed in it. All boys. The club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you make any new friends generally, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well I made all sorts of friends like with - people you know, men and women.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 How did they people meet in those days, how would you make new friends in those says, apart from the ones you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Well you used to meet 'em going walking, a lot used to go walking and you'd - stop and talk and - people in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever bring your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Just one. Just one. He worked with us, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Where would you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 go with}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452  him, anywhere else apart from the Institute?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh - just the same, where I went - where he went I went. And where I went he went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did he play football?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 He used to. Aye.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did your parents meet your friends at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Oh yes, Mac - Mac used to come here. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. They never bothered. Glad to get rid of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No. N}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8355437\charrsid8407452 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 
. Never used to bother with that - half past ten was late enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8864990 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 Did you ever stay out longer than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3157137 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16329306\charrsid8407452 No.
\par }}